    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all project lovers and DIY enthusiasts! This car is the perfect canvas for someone looking to take on a rewarding restoration project. While it currently needs a significant amount of TLC and mechanical attention, it's a fantastic opportunity to own a classic model at an accessible price. If you have the vision and the tools, this could be your next masterpiece!",
