    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly impeccable, mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the leather remains supple and pristine, still carrying that new-car scent, while all electronic features and mechanical components function perfectly. It has been garage-kept and professionally detailed regularly, with a complete service history documenting its pampered life. Buyers can expect a vehicle that requires zero immediate investment and offers a like-new driving experience.",
      "price": 49500.0,
