    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle preserved in true showroom condition. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards, offering an unrivaled driving experience that mirrors its original factory delivery. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, every detail reflects a history of climate-controlled storage and expert care. Mechanically beyond reproach and aesthetically perfect, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019ve decided it\u2019s finally time to let someone else enjoy this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one\u2014honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Whether you're heading out for a weekend cruise or just want something that turns heads at every stoplight, this is the one. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and it runs like an absolute dream. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for acquisition is a meticulously curated E92 M3, a pinnacle of the naturally aspirated S65 V8 era. This specimen features a surgically precise DCT calibration and has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including treated rod bearings and upgraded throttle actuators to ensure peak thermal efficiency and valvetrain longevity. The chassis dynamics have been sharpened via Ohlins Road & Track dampers, reducing unsprung mass while maintaining a compliant rebound profile. Finished in Alpine White with an unblemished carbon fiber roof, the structural integrity is matched only by the visceral acoustics of the Akrapovi\u010d titanium exhaust system. This is a zero-compromise, turn-key machine for the discerning pilot who demands linear power delivery and telepathic steering feedback. Mint throughout, with a documented service history that reads like a technical manual.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless. Showroom fresh. Zero issues. Best price on the market. Won't last.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
